#


######################################################################
BEGIN_PGML

Let [`f(x) = [$f]`].

1. Compute [`f(0)`] = [________]{"$c"}

2. Compute [`f(1)`] = [________]{"$fofone"}

3. Simplify [`f(x + 1)`] = [________]{"$fxplus1"}

4. Simplify [`\dfrac{ f(x) - f(0)}{x}`].
   [____________]{"$diffq"}



END_PGML
